 *     	marks if adding multiple folders (e.g -s "/dir1 /dir2 /dir3")
 *  - SFV generation, --sfv option when importing will generate
 *     	new sfv files and remove existing ones
 *  - + --nowrite, acts normally except it does no actual writing
 *  	(including SFV gen)
